## R code repository for Path analysis with selection study on life-history traits under two thermal conditions with Korean Capsella bursa-pastoris populations.
## Manuscript Title (Draft) Developmental Plastic life-history pathways but conserved selection under temperature variations in Korean populations of Capsella bursa-pastoris

## This repository accompanies the manuscripts: 
## Eujin Kim, Byunwook Choi, and Eunsuk Kim
